description: A React functional component for managing Jira projects, including searching and creating projects via API calls, with UI elements and state management.

methods.name: search
methods.description: Performs a search for Jira projects using provided tenant ID, connector ID, and query, updating the result or error state.

methods.name: create
methods.description: Creates a new Jira project with the specified tenant ID and query name, handling success or error states.
